1) UDP-filter does not (yet) support regular expression matching of filters and domain names. Fixed as of version 0.2
2) UDP-filter does not (yet) support more granular geocoded data then the current country level. Fixed as of version 0.2 
3) The MaxMind City Geo database is not yet supported. Fixed as of version 0.2
4) IP6 address filtering is not yet supported.
5) Geolookup of IP6 addresses is not yet supported.
6) Add SHA1 hash of ip addresses
7) Chain different geo-levels together
8) Add longitude latitude
